headline: Best Stock to Buy Right Now: Costco vs. Realty Income
summary: Costco (NASDAQ: COST) operates nearly 900 club stores around the world.  What does Costco do?  Costco operates club stores, which means that its customers pay an annual membership fee that gives them the privilege of shopping in a Costco store.
